Before you can connect Alexa with Toshiba (ML-EM34P(SS)) microwave oven, please kindly follow below steps:
1. Download "MSmartHome" app from Google Play or App Store;
2. Sign up or sign in with your MSmartHome account;
3. Setup the device with your "MSmartHome" app, and make sure you can control it by the app;
4. Open Alexa app, search "Toshiba iMicrowave" skill and enable it by signing in with the same ID you used in "MsmartHome" app.
5. When setup is ready, try ask Alexa to control your Toshiba (ML-EM34P(SS)) microwave oven.
